{"parse":{"title":"Pablo's Inferno","pageid":4534084,"revid":840675277,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"width:22em;width: 24em; background: #f2f9ff;\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #99c2ff;\">Pablo</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/File:Pablo1cover.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Pablo1cover.JPG\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/aa/Pablo1cover.JPG/200px-Pablo1cover.JPG\" width=\"200\" height=\"316\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/a/aa/Pablo1cover.JPG 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"253\" data-file-height=\"400\" /></a><div><i>Pablo's Inferno</i> Issue One <br />Art by <a href=\"/wiki/Rhode_Montijo\" title=\"Rhode Montijo\">Rhode Montijo</a></div></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #99c2ff;\">Publication information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 40%;\"><a href=\"/wiki/First_appearance\" title=\"First appearance\">First appearance</a></th><td>\n<i>Pablo's Inferno #1</i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 40%;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Comics_creators\" title=\"Category:Comics creators\">Created by</a></th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Rhode_Montijo\" title=\"Rhode Montijo\">Rhode Montijo</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #99c2ff;\">In-story information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 40%;\">Alter ego</th><td>\nPablo</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 40%;\">Team affiliations</th><td>\n<i>Quetzal</i>, <i>El Calambre</i></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>Pablo's Inferno</b></i> is a five-issue <a href=\"/wiki/Alternative_comics\" title=\"Alternative comics\">indie comic</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Limited_series_(comics)\" title=\"Limited series (comics)\">limited series</a> created and produced by <a href=\"/wiki/Rhode_Montijo\" title=\"Rhode Montijo\">Rhode Montijo</a>. The comic owes its title to <i><a href=\"/wiki/Inferno_(Dante)\" title=\"Inferno (Dante)\">Inferno</a></i>, the first <a href=\"/wiki/Cantica\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cantica\">cantica</a> of <a href=\"/wiki/Dante_Alighieri\" title=\"Dante Alighieri\">Dante Alighieri</a>'s <i><a href=\"/wiki/Divine_Comedy\" title=\"Divine Comedy\">Divine Comedy</a></i>, and according to Montijo is something of a parody:\n</p>\n<table class=\"cquote pullquote\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse; border: none; background-color: transparent; width: auto;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: top; border: none; color: #B2B7F2; font-size: 40px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, Times, serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: .6em; text-align: left; padding: 10px 10px;\">\u201c\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; border: none; padding: 4px 10px;\"><i>My friend Dan Chapman, and I, just brainstormed. He knew that I liked to draw monsters, so we came up with the idea of what if there was a little kid who went to hell...just an excuse to draw monsters...it\u2019s kind of like a parody of \u201cDante\u2019s Inferno.\" We ripped on the title and made it a comedic \u201cDante\u2019s Inferno.</i><sup id=\"cite_ref-kaos2000.net_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-kaos2000.net-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: bottom; border: none; color: #B2B7F2; font-size: 40px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, Times, serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: .6em; text-align: right; padding: 10px 10px;\">\u201d\n</td></tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Plot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Plot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Film_Possibilities\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Film Possibilities</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Plot\">Plot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Pablo%27s_Inferno&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Plot\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The comic follows the story of Pablo, a young boy whose life is ended in an unfortunate hit-and-run accident, ends up in <a href=\"/wiki/Hell\" title=\"Hell\">hell</a> and has to traverse the <a href=\"/wiki/Underworld\" title=\"Underworld\">underworld</a> in search of answers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Along the way he meets several colorful characters such as Quetzal, an ancient Aztec god, and El Calambre, the ghost of a once-famous masked wrestler.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Film_Possibilities\">Film Possibilities</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Pablo%27s_Inferno&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Film Possibilities\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>As the comic's popularity continued to grow, Montijo was often questioned on the possibility of a Pablo's Inferno film adaption. Although open to the idea, he is doubtful of the outcome:\n</p>\n<table class=\"cquote pullquote\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse; border: none; background-color: transparent; width: auto;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: top; border: none; color: #B2B7F2; font-size: 40px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, Times, serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: .6em; text-align: left; padding: 10px 10px;\">\u201c\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; border: none; padding: 4px 10px;\"><i>Some people have seen it and they like it, but they think it\u2019s too big in scope. Some people are a little afraid of it. But I would love to, some day.</i><sup id=\"cite_ref-kaos2000.net_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-kaos2000.net-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: bottom; border: none; color: #B2B7F2; font-size: 40px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, Times, serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: .6em; text-align: right; padding: 10px 10px;\">\u201d\n</td></tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Pablo%27s_Inferno&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-kaos2000.net-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-kaos2000.net_1-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-kaos2000.net_1-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.kaos2000.net/interviews/rhodemontijo/\">KAOS2000 Magazine interview with Rhode Montijo</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pablosinferno.com/comics.html\">Pablo's Inferno&#160;: Comics</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Pablo%27s_Inferno&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pablosinferno.com\">Official Website</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pablosinferno.com/blog\">Pablo's Inferno Blog</a></li></ul>\n<table class=\"metadata plainlinks stub\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:transparent\"><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Comiclogo.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stub icon\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/Comiclogo.svg/32px-Comiclogo.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/Comiclogo.svg/48px-Comiclogo.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/Comiclogo.svg/64px-Comiclogo.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"106\" data-file-height=\"109\" /></a></td><td><i>This <a href=\"/wiki/Comics\" title=\"Comics\">comics</a>-related article is a <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Stub\" title=\"Wikipedia:Stub\">stub</a>. You can help Wikipedia by <a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Pablo%27s_Inferno&amp;action=edit\">expanding it</a>.</i><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\" style=\"position: absolute; right: 15px; display: none;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:Comics-stub\" title=\"Template:Comics-stub\"><abbr title=\"View this template\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:Comics-stub\" title=\"Template talk:Comics-stu